  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This open-label, randomized, two-period, two-treatment (single doses of 7.5 mg hetrombopag
      fasted or fed), crossover study was conducted to evaluate the effect of a high-fat meal on
      the pharmacokinetics of hetrombopag and mass balance study in 12 healthy subjects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Completed</overall_status>
  <start_date>March 2014</start_date>
  <completion_date type="Actual">April 2014</completion_date>
  <primary_completion_date type="Actual">April 2014</primary_completion_date>
